   "id": "6c53b0f0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Pipeline Automation & Rate Limiting (Block 4)\n",
    "The next cell executes our live data pull using target coordinates for Oakville, ON. \n",
    "\n",
    "* **Rate Limit Enforcement:** Because Ontario 511 uses IP-based throttling (maximum 10 calls per 60 seconds), we explicitly introduce a `time.sleep(6)` buffer between tests to safeguard our local engineering environment from temporary server bans."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": None,
   "id": "94c199e4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Set up test coordination for Oakville, Ontario\n",
    "oakville_lat = 43.4501\n",
    "oakville_lon = -79.6829\n",
    "\n",
    "# Trigger step-by-step pipeline execution\n",
    "live_weather = get_live_weather(oakville_lat, oakville_lon)\n",
    "time.sleep(2) # Minor buffer\n",
    "\n",
    "live_events = get_ontario_511_events()\n",
    "time.sleep(2) # Minor buffer\n",
    "\n",
    "live_conditions = get_ontario_road_conditions()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n--- Pipeline Run Summary ---\")\n",
    "print(f\"Weather Object: {live_weather is not None}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Alerts Collected: {len(live_events) if live_events else 0}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Condition Reports Collected: {len(live_conditions) if live_conditions else 0}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nEnforcing 6-second cooldown to respect 511 rate limit...\")\n",
    "time.sleep(6)\n",
    "print(\"Safe to run subsequent cells.\")"
   ]
  },
