    "# Historical Dataset Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)\n",
    "Now that the live streams are ready, we analyze our historical baseline data (`traffic_collision_data.xlsx`) sourced from the Toronto Police Annual Statistical Report, as well as new datasets from Seattle Department of Transportation and UK Department for Transport.\n",
    "\n",
    "We check:\n",
    "* Data dimensions and high-level structure.\n",
    "* Null/Missing data vectors (critical for data cleaning choices).\n",
    "* **Class Imbalance** inside the accident severity target column."
   ]
  },
  {
